</style><p>ANYCOLOR 于 2 月 5 日宣布，由于“ <em><a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">屡次违反合同以及在 SNS 上进行误导性虚假陈述和行为</a></em>”，该公司已终止与 Seren Ryugetsu 的合同。此外，该公司还受到海外VTuber观众和粉丝的激烈批评，包括<a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-announced-minor-financial-impact-from-nijisanji-en-new-selen-tatsuki-terminated/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">IR公告称<em>对业务结果的影响极小</em>，</a>而观众也对Dokibird表示支持。 ・我们不仅在扩大影响力不仅针对粉丝，也针对各种公司和组织。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="n3FXUx8d9i"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-elira-pendora-expressed-criticized-selen-tatsuki-and-support-for-anycolor/">NIJISANJI EN（新）VTuber Elira Pendora批评Seren Ryugetsu并表示支持ANYCOLOR</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“NIJISANJI EN（新）VTuber Elira Pendora批评Seren Ryugetsu并表示支持ANYCOLOR” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-elira-pendora-expressed-criticized-selen-tatsuki-and-support-for-anycolor/embed/#?secret=hOcNNzDt8e#?secret=n3FXUx8d9i" data-secret="n3FXUx8d9i" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="mbF9qYEyfH"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-announced-minor-financial-impact-from-nijisanji-en-new-selen-tatsuki-terminated/">ANYCOLOR NIJISANJI EN（新）宣布取消Seren Ryugetsu合同对业绩的影响将很小</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ANYCOLOR NIJISANJI EN（新）宣布，Seren Ryugetsu 合同取消对业绩的影响将很小” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp